Class Helper

java.lang.Object
Helper
public class Helper
extends java.lang.Object
This is the helper class, the point of this class is create a way for the GUI to interact with the other classes, including flocksim, main, etc. In other words, this allowed there to be a constant flow of communication between GUI and main. Documentation Statement: none used
Author:
C22Andrew.Lee
